<view class="container">
  <view class="header">
    <view class="title">连连看</view>
    <view class="subtitle">找到两张相同图案即可消除</view>
  </view>

  <view class="info-bar">
    <view class="info-item">
      <text class="label">关卡</text>
      <text class="value">{{level}}</text>
    </view>
    <view class="info-item">
      <text class="label">难度</text>
      <text class="value">{{difficulty}}</text>
    </view>
    <view class="info-item">
      <text class="label">步数</text>
      <text class="value">{{moves}}</text>
    </view>
    <view class="info-item">
      <text class="label">剩余时间</text>
      <text class="value">{{timeLeft}}s</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="board" style="grid-template-columns: repeat({{cols}}, 1fr);">
    <view
      class="tile {{item.status}} {{pathIndices.indexOf(index) >= 0 ? 'path' : ''}}"
      wx:for="{{tiles}}"
      wx:key="index"
      data-index="{{index}}"
      bindtap="onTileTap"
    >
      <text wx:if="{{item.status !== 'removed'}}">{{item.icon}}</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="buttons">
    <button class="btn" bindtap="restart">重新开始</button>
  </view>

  <view class="tips">
    <text>提示：点击两张相同图案的牌即可消除，遵循连连看连线规则（最多两次拐弯）。通关后可以继续挑战下一关，关卡无限。</text>
  </view>
</view>

